title: Top Nazi: SS General Karl Wolff
description:
Top Nazi: SS General Karl Wolff, The Man Between Hitler and Himmler - Jochen von Lang [epub]

As Heinrich Himmler's adjutant and direct representative to Adolf Hitler, Karl Wolff stood at the top of the Nazi hierarchy. Involved in some of the most gruesome Nazi misdeeds Wolff was promoted to general and then SS and Police chief in Italy in 1943-1945, when Hitler ordered him to kidnap Pope Pius XII. Wolff also negotiated the secret surrender with Alan Dulles in 'Operation Sunrise'
